race.comment: GRAFTERBURNERS (1) returned in fine fashion with a dominant Eagle Farm victory and did get up to Group 1 level when last in work. Looks to have a bit of class over most of these and another strong showing would not surprise. NINJA (3) resumes here but the form he showed in his first campaign was good enough for a race of this calibre. Can run a big race while fresh. DAMIEN (2) is a winner over this track and trip, strips fitter second-up and draws the inside alley. Ticks a few boxes. MIDNIGHT SPIRIT (7) gets the deadly Gollan/Maloney combination and can feature with any luck in running.
